\id 1TI TEKE-TYEE
\h 1 TIMOTE
\toc3 1 Tim
\toc2 1 Timote
\toc1 MUKAANA A POOLE WU A NSOMO KUNDAA TIMOTE
\mt2 Mukaana wu a nsomo kundaa
\mt1 Timote
\imt1 OSOMO
\ip Wu me mukaana wu a nsomo wu ósono Poole kunda Timote. Poole áli agyene ku Lisitere mu oyitsala Nsia yi Mbwe. Oko me ku áli okakala Timote. Nde ábaana onama nzili a Kriste ŋa mbihi a ŋa ágyughu nde Ndagha a Nzaami yi ókaluo Poole. Nde ádzie mansa malagha ya Poole ya básala emõ ya nde.
\ip Mu matala ma ókagyughu Poole ti bakriste baba mu bvulu limõ bwunu we lini bali mu okatyeghe Nzaami ebughu, bwunu we oli a mandagha oko, nde áli a epfu kii okagweghe Timote mu oyigwa bo maluo. Obo me bu ógweghe Poole Timote ku Efedze mpaala ayigwa bakwuru ba libwunu baba oko mpama. Ngu oko Timote ágyagha mukaana wu. Mu mukaana wu Poole álibili nde mweẽ mu oyilyele kundaa banga-a-kana ti basa mayele ŋa nkulu a ba baakaluo baara mandagha mama lisobo ya Nsia yi Mbwe. Poole ályele ndehe si nki bipfu banga-a-kana bafaana okala a bye munsa mabwunu ma Nzaami, ya bunu bo bafaana okasuolo bakwuru ba libwunu li bo.
\ib
\iot Bu me bu baakakaba mukaana wu:
\io1 - Mamboro (\xt 1.1-2\xt*).
\io1 - Bu ofaana okala laama li banga-a-kana (\xt 1.3–3.13\xt*).
\io1 - Mandagha ma básweghe mu nzili yi liikanama bihi (\xt 3.14–4.5\xt*).
\io1 - Poole ágwi Timote maluo (\xt 4.6–6.21\xt*).
\c 1
\s1 Mamboro
\p 
\v 1 Me Poole, ntumu a Yiisu-Kriste mu litumu li Nzaami Mubvwuhu a bihi, ya lili Yiisu-Kriste, wu li emiini e bihi,
\v 2 nsono mukaana wu kundaa Timote, nkara a mwana a me mu kana. Nyaã ti bwehe, nyiĩ ya edzuunu bi bifi kundaa Nzaami Taara ya kundaa Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste bikala ya we!
\s1 Osa mayele mu maluo mama mpya
\p 
\v 3 Ti bwunu a bu ángwi me we litumu mu matala ma ákangye me ku Masedwane ti kala ŋa Efedze, mpaala we kahaba baara babake mu onyaã okatsala nsia a maluo mama mpya
\v 4 ya mu onyaã osa mukolo mu masaba ya mu okataŋana mankwumu ma bankagha-kwuru ma magwene a masini. Mandagha mamo maakaburu munsohobo ŋa ebini kii osala esala e Nzaami ki baakasa mu kana.
\v 5 Mupfunu a litumu lilo ngu osuo dzyi li lifi mu mukolo wu a tse-tse, mu bitsimi bi bibwe ya mu kana lili ngaŋma.
\v 6 Baara babake, bu baabihi onama mandagha mamo, baagyene mu okabulusa nkele yi gwene a mubwughu.
\v 7 Bo badzyi okala baluo ba mikyene, lo bo bomo ka bali mu okabaghala mandagha ma bali mu okalyele bo o, ngu okala mandagha ma baakalyele bo ya enziini ti mo mali mama ngaŋma.
\p 
\v 8 Bihi-a-be ligyili osoolo ti mikyene mili mibwe kala ti basalala mye bu ofaana.
\v 9 Bihi-a-be si lisoolo ti mikyene ka bágwi mye mu nkooro a baara baba nsumu o, lo mu nkooro a baara ba baagwene okanama Mikyene ya ba baakagyighili mandagha ma mabi, baara ba babi ya banga-a-masumu, baara ba baagwene okagwa Nzaami budziri ya ba baagwene okagwa bilogho bibi ngili budziri, ba baakadzwa bataara babo ya ba baakadzwa bangughu babo, ba baakadzwa baara,
\v 10 baara banga-a-enkwunu, babaghala ba baakabvughu mbughu ya banganda babaghala, minta-nkaala mi bankana, banga a mpya, ba baakalaba mukihi wu a mpya, ya baara bwohono ba baakatemene maluo mama ngaŋma ngangala.
\v 11 Obo me bu oli nsia yi mbwe yi a nsia a Nzaami nga a esee, nsia yi mbwe yi baagwi me.
\s1 Poole bvurulu matuono kundaa Nzaami
\p 
\v 12 Me mbvurulu matuono kundaa Yiisu-Kriste mfumu a bihi, nde wu aagwi me lileene, mu kuulu nde aamono ti me ndi mbwuru wu bakughu osa kana mu nde bu aasi ti me nsala esala e nde,
\v 13 me wuulu nsomo áakantsua Nzaami, áakamwehẽ banga-a-kana kimini, nga a eŋma. Lo Nzaami aamono me nyiĩ mu kuulu me áakangyighili mandagha mamo kunsa nzi-nzimini, wene a kana.
\v 14 Ya bwehe bu Mfumu a bihi bu bulagha buumoŋono mu me, nde aagwi me kana ya dzyi bi biikafa mu bumõ ya Yiisu-Kriste.
\v 15 Ndagha yi yili yi a ngaŋma ya yiili baara bwohono bakughu okihi yo: Yiisu-Kriste aagyi ŋa nsie mu oyabvwuhu banga-a-masumu. Ya me, me ndi mbwuru wu a nsomo ŋa kara li banga-a-masumu.
\v 16 Lo Nzaami aamono me nyiĩ, mpaala mu me, wu ndi wu a nsomo, Yiisu-Kriste asuo mukolo a nde wu munene ti anga efaana kundaa babo ba baasa kana mu nde mpaala babagha laama lili mibvu ya mibvu.
\v 17 Nyaã nsia ya budziri bikala kundaa Mukogho wu matala mwohono, wu aagwene okamoŋono, wu aagwene okakpa, Nzaami yini a mumõ, mu mibvu ya mibvu! «Aamene!»
\s1 Odzwana mvulu yi mbwe
\p 
\v 18 Timote mwana a me, me ntumu we mu odzwana mvulu yi mbwe, ti bwunu a bu oli mandagha ma ótswama olyele mibighili mu nkooro a we, mpaala we bagha mpini mu mo,
\v 19 we bukebe kana ya bitsimi bi bibwe. Bitsimi bi bibwe bibye, babake baatsili bye ya baadzihibi kana li bo.
\v 20 Imene ya Alesandere bali ŋa kara li baara babo. Me aanyaghala bo ŋa myaã mi Satana mpaala bo banyaã ofirikatsua Nzaami.
\c 2
\s1 Osamana mu nkooro a baara bwohono
\p 
\v 1 Mu obo, nsomo-a-nsomo me gwi be mpama mu akaluomo, mu okasamana, mu ookabuono ya mu okabvurulu matuono kundaa Nzaami mu baara bwohono,
\v 2 mu nkooro a mikogho ya mu nkooro a baara bwohono ba bali a litumu, mpaala bihi-a-be likala a bumweẽ bubu edzuunu ya bubu pii, mu enzaami kyehene ya budziri bwohono.
\v 3 Obo oli bubwe ya Nzaami wu li Mubvwuhu a bihi-a-be aakadzyi obo.
\v 4 Nde dzyi ti baara bwohono babvwughu ya bakala a ligyahaba li engaŋma.
\q1 
\v 5 Mu kuulu Nzaami li yini a mumõ,
\q1 ya mbwuru wu aakabvurulu endughu ŋa kara li Nzaami ya baara li yini a mumõ,
\q1 mbwuru munde me Yiisu-Kriste,
\q1 
\v 6 nde wu áafiri ekolo mu nyuru a ndeme mu nkooro a baara bwohono:
\q1 Bubo me bumpughulu bu básuo mu matala ma ósuolo Nzaami.
\m 
\v 7 Me mu obo Nzaami ásuolo me mu okala wu aakata mukwughu, ntumu (me engaŋma ndyele, me ka mpfiri mpya o) ya muluo kundaa baala ka bali ba-Dzwife o, mu kana ya mu engaŋma.
\s1 Babaghala ya bakaha mu libwunu li Nzaami
\p 
\v 8 Mu obo, me ndzyi ti babaghala bakasamana Nzaami mu bibini byehene, bakaseene myaã mimi ngili ku yulu, wene a nkehe, wene a minsohobo.
\p 
\v 9 Bumõ si kundaa bakaha, me ndzyi ti bo bakalaha nda-ndaha yi budziri, yiili baara ka bakughu omono budzwa mu yo o, wene a mubili a nyuru. Bo ka bafaana okakuru bibara bi mfu o, ka bafaana okalaha milwu ya nsia bibi mu oore o, ngu okala nsia, bwunu we binkuru bibi ntala yi alagha.
\v 10 Lo bo bafaana okasuo bigyighili bi bibwe, ti bwunu a bu ofaana kundaa bakaha ba baakalyele ti bo baakasamana Nzaami.
\p 
\v 11 Nyaã ti mu matala mama ogyighi mandagha ma Nzaami, mukaha akala pii ya kunsa okihi kwohono kuu litumu li ba baakaluo nde.
\v 12 Me ka ngwi mukaha muswa wu oluo o, ngu okala mu okala a litumu ŋa yulu a baghala. Nyaã nde akala pii.
\v 13 Mu kuulu me Adã Nzaami átswama obuo ya ŋa nseele nde ábuo Ebve.
\v 14 Ya ntaala ka ápfiri Adã o, lo mukaha nde ápfiri, me mukaha áabagha ebili kundaa Nzaami bu átsumunu ngili.
\v 15 Lo nde sa akarabvwughu ŋa aaburu nde, kala ti nde kebe kana, dzyi, kala ti nde li wu báseme ya bátwulu mu libee mu osalala Nzaami ya nzya-nzyara yi mbwe.
\c 3
\s1 Bambiri ba libwunu li Nzaami
\p 
\v 1 Ndagha yi yili yi a ngaŋma: Kala ti mbwuru dzyi okala mumbiri a libwunu li Nzaami, ekye esala ki ebwe nde adzyi.
\v 2 Me mu obo, mumbiri a libwunu li Nzaami faana okala mbwuru wuulu ka baabagha ndagha yi baasyeme nde o, mulumu a mukaha yini a mutsyini, wu li a nzya-nzyara yi a faana ya yi a budziri, akala mbwuru wu aakuru nyuru ya wu li a nzya-nzyara yi mbwe, akala mbwuru wu akabwana a banzyi, mbwuru wu kughu oluo.
\v 3 Anyaã okala enkolo-mala, anyaã okala a nzuŋu, lo akala mbwuru wu aakasa kuulu ti baara bakala mu eyiẽ, mbwuru wu aakasa ti baara bakala mu edzuunu ya wu gwene a ntono a nzi.
\v 4 Nde faana otumu nzo a ndeme bubwe ya baana ba nde bafaana okala mu litumu li nde mu budziri bwohono.
\v 5 Mu kuulu, kala ti mbwuru ka soolo otumu nzo a ndeme o, bunu a bo nde aatumu Libwunu li Nzaami?
\v 6 Nde anyaã okala mbwuru wu munyaghara mu enzaami, mfangolo ligwagha lidzwi nde mihi ya nde somo mu mumfwunu a dyabulu.
\v 7 Ofaana si ti baara ba bali ku mbala a libwunu basuo bumpughulu bu bubwe mu nde, mpaala baara banyaã otsaala nde ya nde anyaã okogholo mu myere mi dyabulu.
\s1 Basala ba Nzaami
\p 
\v 8 Bumõ si, basala ba Nzaami bafaana okala baara baba budziri ya banga a engaŋma. Banyaã okala binkolo-mala ya okadzyi busini bu baakabagha mu manzili ma mabi.
\v 9 Bo bafaana okakebe mu bitsimi bibi tse-tse mansweghe ma kana ma ósuo Nzaami.
\v 10 Nsomo, bafaana oluhu bo mu bigyeele ya ŋa nseele, kala ti ka babagha ndagha yi baasyeme bo o, bo bakughu osala esala e Nzaami.
\p 
\v 11 Bakaha si bafaana okala baba budziri, ba bagwene a makuhu, ba bali a nzya-nzyara yi faana ya yi a budziri. Bo bafaana okala baara baala mu nswe ndagha bakughu osa kana mu bo.
\v 12 Musala a Nzaami faana okala a mukala yini a mutsyini, ya nde faana okatumu baana ya nzo a nde bubwe.
\v 13 Mu kuulu, baara ba baakasala esala e Nzaami bubwe, sa bagwa bo budziri ya bo sa bakala a emiini ki elagha mu kana li lili mu Yiisu-Kriste.
\s1 Mansweghe ma mpaana a enzaami
\p 
\v 14 Me nsono we mandagha ma mu emiini kiili ti edzi-dzighi me sa ngyamono we.
\v 15 Lo kala ti me ka mbaangya o, we sa soolo bunu a bo we aadzyara munsa nzo a Nzaami, yili Libwunu li Nzaami wu a mweẽ, kwii li linene ya li ookasiŋi engaŋma.
\v 16 Ya oli ngaŋma ti mansweghe ma mpaana a enzaami mali ma manene:
\q1 Yiisu-Kriste ámoŋono ti anga mbwuru,
\q1 bási nde mbwuru wu bunsumu mu Mufulu a Ngili,
\q1 nde ámoŋono kundaa bangye-yulu,
\q1 bátsala nsia a nde kundaa bikaana byehene,
\q1 baara ba nsie bási kana mu nde,
\q1 Bágyene a nde ku yulu munsa nsia.
\c 4
\s1 Maluo mama mpya
\p 
\v 1 Ankoho, Mufulu a Ngili li mu olyele mu mpere ti mu matala mama masini, ndaama a baara sa batsili kana li bo mu onama mifulu mimi mpya ya maluo ma maakafa kundaa mifulu mi mibi,
\v 2 mu bumpibi bubu embili-a-mbili ki banga a mpya ba bási elyimi mu bitsimi bi bo mu esyeẽ ki ebie mu mbaa.
\v 3 Bo baakalighi baara okie ya baakagwa bo mangili maala banyaã okadza bilogho bibike, ankoho Nzaami ágyighili bye mu kuulu ba baakasa kana bakadza bye mu okabvurulu matuono bu basoolo engaŋma.
\v 4 Mu kuulu byehene bi ógyighili Nzaami bili bi bibwe, ya ka oli a si emõ ki baatsili o, lo bafaana odza kye mu okabvurulu matuono,
\v 5 mu kuulu mu ndagha Nzaami ya mu lisamana baakasa ti bye byehene bikala bibi ngili.
\s1 Nzaami li mubvwuhu a baara bwohono
\p 
\v 6 Kala ti we luo mandagha mwohono ma kundaa bandughu mu kana, we sa kala musala a Yiisu-Kriste wu mubwe, wu baakabuŋunu mu mandagha mama kana ya mu maluo ma mabwe ma aakanama we matala mwohono.
\v 7 Lo we bihi masaba ma magwene a mupfunu maala ka mali mama kana o, masaba ma biŋmini bi bakaha.
\m Lo we sa mpini mu okala a enzaami ki ebwe.
\v 8 Mu kuulu bimpa bi biikagwa nyuru mpini ka bili a ndaana yi alagha o. Lo enzaami eli a mupfunu mu myehene: Kye eli a misiini mimi laama lili lolo ya lili bitsughu bi biigya.
\v 9 Ndagha yi yili yi a ngaŋma ya yiili baara bwohono bakughu okihi yo:
\v 10 Kala ti bihi-a-be lili mu okamono mpara ya lili mu okadzwana mvulu, mu kuulu bihi-a-be liisi emiini mu Nzaami wu a mweẽ, wu li mubvwuhu a baara bwohono, ya bvulu-bvulu banga-a-kana.
\p 
\v 11 Mamo mandagha ma faana otumu ya oluo we baara.
\s1 Efaana kundaa banga-a-kana
\p 
\v 12 Mbwuru anyaã otsaala bufulu bu we! Lo we kala efaana kundaa banga-a-kana mu mbiili, mu nzya-nzyara, mu dzyi, mu kana ya mu mukolo wu a tse-tse.
\p 
\v 13 Tee mu matala ma akala aangya me, sa makpa mu okantaã Bisono bibi ngili ŋa nkulu a baara bwohono, mu okagwa babake mpama ya mu okaluo.
\v 14 Ka meŋene ekaba kii bwehe bu Nzaami ki eli mu we o, ekaba ki bágwi we mu nzili a libighi ya ŋa ónaã we emvuŋunu ki bakwuru ba libwunu myaã ŋa yulu a mutswi.
\v 15 Sa mandagha mamo mu mukolo mumõ, gwa nyuru a we yohono mu esala ki mpaala okulu o we omoŋono ŋa mihi mi baara bwohono.
\v 16 Kahala mihi mu nyuru a weme ya mu maluo ma we. Sa mukama munsa mandagha mamo. Mu kuulu, we bu si obo, we weme sa bvwuhu ya baara ba baagyughu wehe si sa babvwughu.
\c 5
\s1 Mi bafaana osa kundaa baara ba libwunu
\p 
\v 1 Ka akasyeme eŋmini mu ebaghala o, lo kagwa nde mpama ti anga we li mu okagwa taara a weme mpama. Aakagwolo minkuru-mbala ti anga baana ba ngughu a we,
\v 2 bakaha ba bakwuru ti anga bangughu ba we, batughu ti anga bankele ba we, ya mukolo wu a tse-tse.
\s1 Bapfiili ba bakaha
\p 
\v 3 Aakagwa bapfiili ba bakaha, maa ngu bapfiili, ba bali a nzala a libaha budziri.
\v 4 Kala ti mupfiili wu mukaha li a baana bwunu we bateghele, nyaã ti nsomo baana ya bateghele babo basuo enzaami e bo mu manzo ma bomo ya mu okabvurulu bubwe bu ósi bo biburu bi bo. Obo me bu ookadzyi Nzaami.
\v 5 Lo maa ngu mupfiili wu mukaha wu aasyili ngasighi, wu aasi emiini e nde mu Nzaami, nde aakasa mukama mu okasamana ya mu okabuono mpyibi ya mwiĩ.
\v 6 Lo mupfiili wu mukaha wu li kunsa bisee bi nsie nde li wu a kpi, ngu okala ti nde li nkini mweẽ.
\v 7 Mimye mikele mi faana otswa we bapfiili ba bakaha, mu kuulu banyaã obagha ndagha yi baasyeme bo.
\v 8 Ya kala ti mbwuru ka aakabaha badzighi ba nde o, bvulu-bvulu baara ba bali mu nzo nde, lo nde aatunu kana li nde, ya nde bvulu bubi ya mbwuru wu gwene a kana.
\p 
\v 9 Mu osono nkwumu a mupfiili wu mukaha mu mukaana wu a emvuŋunu ki bapfiili, nde faana okala a bamvulu obaana makwumu-masemene (60) tee ku yulu, ya wu áali mukala a baghala yini a mutsyini.
\v 10 Baara bafaana osuo bumpughulu bu bigyighili bi nde bi bibwe: Nde aakwuhu baana ba nde, nde aakabwana a baara mu nzo a nde, nde aakaswagha myili mi baba ngili, nde aakabaha babo ba bali mu mpara ya nde aakasalala bigyighili bi bibwe.
\p 
\v 11 Lo we ka sono mankwumu ma bapfiili ba bali nkini batughu o. Mu kuulu, mu matala ma baakala a bo nzala a ofirikie, bo baakabihi Kriste.
\v 12 Obo me bu baakasomo bo mu mumfwunu mu kuulu bo baakatunu mukihi wu bálaba nsomo.
\v 13 Ndagha yinke me yi, bo bu bagwene a esala ki baasa, bo baakabulugye mu manzo ma baara, lo ka yini a mu nkooro a ku bagwene a bo esala o, lo mu nkooro a nkele ya embili-a-mbili e bo. Bo baakabulubili mu mandagha maala ka bafaana obili mu mo o.
\p 
\v 14 Mu obo, me ndzyi ti bapfiili ba bali nkini batughu bafaana ofirikie, bafaana oburu baana, bafaana okala bakaha ba babwe mu manzo, buulu banyaã ogwa mutaara nzili yi obili bubi bu banga-a-kana.
\v 15 Mu kuulu, bapfiili ba bakaha babake ŋa kara li bo baasihi nzili a Mfumu mu onama Satana.
\v 16 Kala ti nga-a-kana wu mukaha li a bapfiili ba bakaha mu badzighi ba nde, nyaã nde abaha bo ya leme lilo linyaã ogya ku yulu a libwunu li Nzaami, buulu libwunu li Nzaami libaha maa ngu bapfiili ba bakaha.
\s1 Bakwuru ba libwunu
\p 
\v 17 Nyaã ti bakwuru ba libwunu ba baakatumu bubwe bagwa bo budziri bu bulagha ya bu bufaana, bvulu-bvulu ba baakamono mpara mu esala kii okatsala nsia a Ndagha a Nzaami ya kii okaluo.
\v 18 Mu kuulu, Ndagha a Nzaami yiikalyele ti: «We ka kuru muŋma a ngoomo wu li mu okasala mu matala mama okele bimburu o,» ya: Musala faana obagha mufuru a nde.
\v 19 Ka kihi o ti bayafwunu mukwuru a libwunu kundaa we, kala ti ka «ŋa nkulu a bampughulu buolo bwunu we batere o.»
\v 20 Ŋa mihi mi baara bwohono, aakasyeme ba baakasa masumu, buulu babake babagha nzalamweẽ.
\p 
\v 21 Ŋa nkulu a Nzaami, ŋa nkulu a Yiisu-Kriste ya ŋa nkulu a bangye-yulu ba básuolo, me ntswi we mikele mi mu okasalala mandagha mamo mu bunsumu wene a munsuolo a bidzili.
\v 22 Ka naã myaã mu maswa-maswa ŋa yulu a mutswi a mbwuru o, mara we kala mu mfwunu a masumu ma mbwuru mukimi. We weme, aakakala wu a tse-tse.
\p 
\v 23 Mu nkooro a mila mi miikatswa we matala mwohono ya mabyele mama mu mweẽ, ka akaŋma yini a madza o. Aakaŋma si mana bviini.
\v 24 Masumu ma baara bana maakamoŋono nsomo basa bo mumfwunu. Lo masumu ma baara babake maakamoŋono yini a ŋa mbihi.
\v 25 Bumõ si, bigyighili bi bibwe biikamoŋono ŋa mihi mi baara bwohono, ngu okala bibye biili nkini biimoŋono o, bye ka bikughu osweme o.
\c 6
\s1 Bankana
\p 
\v 1 Nyaã ti baara bwohono ba bali kunsa bunkana bagwa bamfumu ba bo budziri, mpaala banyaã otsaala nkwumu a Nzaami ya maluo ma bihi.
\v 2 Ya bankana ba bali a bamfumu banga-a-kana banyaã okatsaala bamfumu ba bo mu kuulu bo bali bandughu mu kana. Lo bo bafaana okasalala bo ku obvulu bubwe mu kuulu bo bali mu okasalala banga-a-kana ya bandughu ba bo baba mukolo.
\m Mamo ngu mandagha mafaana okaluo we ya okatumu.
\s1 Enzaami kii ngaŋma
\p 
\v 3 Nswe mbwuru wu aakaluo maluo makimi, ya ka li mu okanama mandagha ma mabwe mama Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste o, ya maluo ma mali bwunu a bu oli enzaami,
\v 4 nde ka li a ligyahaba o, mubili a nyuru aadzwi nde mihi. Nde li a bubyele bubu munsohobo ya mumbaŋana. Obo me bu ookagya sughu li mukolo, mitaha, otsaala, ya bitsimi bi bibi,
\v 5 mimbaŋana mi migwene a masini ŋa kara li baara ba bali a mayele obyi. Bo ka basoolo engaŋma o, ya bo baakatsimi ti enzaami eli nzili yi obagha busini.
\p 
\v 6 Ngaŋma, enzaami eli busini bu bunene kundaa munde wu aakamono esee mu yini a bi ali a nde.
\p 
\v 7 Mu kuulu bihi-a-be ka líyabiri elogho mu nsie o,
\q1 bwunu obo si ŋa akala liimaara bihi-a-be ŋa nsie, ka libiri elogho o.
\q1 
\v 8 Kala ti bihi-a-be lili a bi-odza ya binkuru, bihi-a-be lifaana okamono esee mu bye.
\m 
\v 9 Lo babo ba baakadzyi okala a busini, baakabwa mu bigyeele, baakakogholo mu mwere ya mu sughu li mukolo li linene ya li libi li liikasohobo baara kunsa obyi ya odzimini.
\v 10 Mu kuulu ntono a nzi yiikaburu mandagha mwohono ma mabi. Mu nkooro a yo, baara bana baadzimini ya ka baafirisyili a kana o, ya bo baamwehẽ manyuru ma bomo mpara yi alagha.
\s1 Litumu kundaa Timote
\q1 
\v 11 Lo we wu li mbwuru a Nzaami, aakabara mandagha mamo.
\q1 We faana okasagha bunsumu, enzaami, kana,
\q1 dzyi, mukama ya odzuunu.
\q1 
\v 12 We kadzwana mvulu yi mbwe yi a kana,
\q1 dzarala laama lili mibvu ya mibvu li báti we mbili mu lo,
\q1 ya liili we áasuo bumpughulu bu bubwe
\q1 ŋa nkulu a bampughulu balagha.
\p 
\v 13 Ŋa nkulu a Nzaami wu aakagwa byehene bi bili mweẽ laama, ya ŋa nkulu a Yiisu-Kriste wu áasuo bumpughulu mu mbiili yi mbwe yi a kana ŋa busu bu Ponse Pilate, me ngwi we litumu li:
\v 14 Kebe litumu bu kala wene a mpiri, wene a mi baasyeme we, tee mu matala ma oomoŋono Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste.
\v 15 Omoŋono oko sa okala, mu matala ma ókuru Nzaami,
\q1 nga-a-esee, Ibyala nga emõ,
\q1 Mukogho a mikogho
\q1 ya Mfumu a bamfumu,
\q1 
\v 16 yini a nde wuulu ka aakakpa o,
\q1 nde wu aakakala kunsa otsyeme kuulu mbwuru ka kughu osomo oko o,
\q1 otsyeme kuulu mbwuru si mumõ nkini ámaamono o, ya ka kughu omono o.
\q1 Nyaã ti nsia ya lileene bibi mibvu ya mibvu bikala kundaa nde! «Aamene!»
\s1 Bisini
\p 
\v 17 Gwa litumu li kundaa bisini bi bili mu nsie yi banyaã okala a mubili a nyuru, ya banyaã osa emiini e bo mu busini buulu ka buukagyili matala malagha o. Lo bo basa emiini e bo mu Nzaami, nde wu aakagwa bihi bilogho byehene ku olagha mpaala bihi limono esee mu bye.
\v 18 Nyaã bo bakasa bubwe, bakala bisini mu bigyighili bi bibwe, banga-a-kaba, ba baakabaha banganda.
\v 19 Obo bo baakwu busini bu bubwe mu bomo mu bitsughu bi nkulu, mpaala babagha laama lili ngaŋma.
\s1 Mikele mimi masini
\p 
\v 20 A we Timote! Aakakebe mandagha ma baagwi we. Aakabara mbiili yi mukaŋana yi aagwene faana ya kana. Ka akabaŋana mu mi mitala maluo mama ligyahaba lili mpya o.
\v 21 Ndaama a baara yi aakatsimi ti yo yili a ligyahaba lilo, ka yiifirisyili mu nzili a kana o.
\m Nyaã bwehe bu Nzaami bukala ya be!
